    "These two views should be combined to create successful prediction models that form a loop between educational application and empirical research validation, along with AI model development and optimization Ouyang et al (2023); Wu et al (2022); Yang et al (2021).",
    "However, the majority of research on AI prediction models has focused on the creation and improvement of AI models, that is, employing several algorithms to create models with greater predictive accuracy Ouyang et al (2023)."
